# AGENT_REPORT Template

## Compact Report

```json
{
  "verdict": "APPROVED|NEEDS_FIX|BLOCKED|DONE|FIX_REQUIRED|VERIFIED",
  "score": 1,
  "findings": [
    {
      "severity": "CRITICAL|MAJOR|MINOR",
      "file": "path/to/file",
      "line": 1,
      "description": "What is wrong"
    }
  ],
  "selfCritique": "What might still be missing",
  "handoffFile": "{{artifacts.phaseRoot}}/phase-<phase-token>/handoffs/<taskId>/<phase>-detail.md",
  "lessons": [],
  "memoryLessons": []
}
```

## Notes

- `lessons` are task-local observations that stay in state.
- `memoryLessons` are durable lessons worth carrying across sessions.
- Use a handoff file for detailed fix steps, not the compact report body.
